3月7日19:30左右，福建省泉州市鲤城区欣佳酒店发生楼体坍塌。
March 7 around 1930, the Fujian Province Quanzhou City Yinjia Hotel building collapse.
房屋倒塌瞬间视频曝光Play事发后楼内受困71人，另有9人自救逃生泉州市政府官方网站8日发文称，3月7日19时许，鲤城区欣佳酒店发生楼体坍塌事故。
A collapse of a building at the Xinjia Hotel in Lei Cheng occurred at about 1900 hours on March 7, according to the official website of the government of Quanzhou City.
经过摸排，事发后大楼内受困71人（不含自救逃生9人）。
After mapping, the building after the incident trapped 71 people (not including self-help escape 9 people).
事发当晚，省、市、区三级出动吊车、起重机、挖掘机等应急救援车辆43部、消防车辆126部、救护车20部，消防、医务及其他救援人员1000余名。
On the night of the accident, 43 emergency rescue vehicles, 126 fire-fighting vehicles, 20 ambulances and over 1,000 fire-fighting, medical and other rescue personnel were deployed at the provincial, city and district levels.
目前，现场施救工作仍在争分夺秒、全力以赴进行中。
At present, on-the-spot rescue work is still running out of time, go all out.
事故已致4人死亡据应急管理部消息，目前，福建省消防救援总队已投入9个支队的轻重型搜救队、170辆消防车、853名指战员、9头搜救犬及生命探测仪等救援装备，将坍塌现场划分6个救援区域，正在9个作业点全力打通救援通道，同时5个小组持续不断开展生命迹象搜寻。
Four people have died in the accident, according to the Ministry of Emergency Management. At present, the General Fire Rescue Team of Fujian Province has invested nine light and heavy search and rescue teams, 170 fire trucks, 853 military personnel, 9 search and rescue dogs and life-detector rescue equipment.
福建省人民政府调度医疗抢救组共750多人、20辆120急救车，全力做好受伤人员的救治和康复工作。
The medical rescue team of the people's government of Fujian Province has more than 750 people and 20 120 first-aid vehicles.
截至3月8日10时30分，现场已救出42人（其中死亡4人、危重1人、重伤4人）。
As at 1030 hours on 8 March, 42 people had been rescued from the scene (4 dead, 1 in critical condition and 4 seriously injured).
图片来源：人民日报官微国家卫健委：已派专家组支援国家卫健委8日通报称，2020年3月7日晚，福建省泉州市鲤城区一酒店（新冠肺炎密切接触者医学隔离观察点）发生坍塌事故。
Photo: People's Daily Guan Wei National Fitness Commission: A team of experts has been sent to support the National Health Commission reported on the night of March 7, 2020, a hotel in Lei Cheng, Quanzhou City, Fujian Province (close contacts of the New Crown Pneumonia Medical Isolation Observatory) collapsed.
国家卫生健康委高度重视，迅速调派两批国家级医疗卫生应急专家组共18人，支援当地开展伤员救治等卫生应急处置工作。
The National Health Council attaches great importance to the rapid deployment of two national teams of medical and health emergency experts, a total of 18 people, to support the local casualty treatment and other emergency response work.
第一批专家组7日晚从福州、厦门就近派出，由福建医科大学附属协和医院、附属第一医院和厦门大学附属医院的重症医学、创伤骨科、心理干预、院感防控等多专业14名专家组成。
The first group of experts, dispatched from Fuzhou and Xiamen on the night of July 7, was composed of 14 specialists specializing in severe medicine, orthopaedic trauma, psychological intervention and sensory prevention and control, affiliated with Concorde Hospital, affiliated Hospital No. 1 and Xiamen University Hospital of Fujian Medical University.
第二批专家组8日早从广州出发，由中山大学附属第一医院重症医学、神经外科、创伤骨科、胸外科专业4名专家组成。
The second group of experts started from Guangzhou early on the 8th and consisted of 4 experts specializing in severe medicine, neurosurgery, orthopaedics and thoracic surgery.
事故发生后，当地卫生健康部门第一时间启动应急响应，迅速开展伤员转运和医疗救治等工作。
After the accident, the local health authorities immediately activated the emergency response, rapid casualty transit and medical treatment and other work.
福建省卫生健康委负责同志带领省级专家组连夜赶到泉州，指挥协调伤员救治等工作。
Fujian Provincial Health Committee leading the provincial team of experts to Quanzhou overnight, command and coordination of casualty treatment and other work.
目前，事故伤员分别在泉州市4家医院住院治疗。
Currently, the injured are hospitalized in four hospitals in Quanzhou City.
国家、省、市专家组成联合医疗专家组，对伤员逐一会诊评估，实施一人一策，密切监测伤情变化，动态调整完善救治方案，全力救治，同时严格做好救治医务人员传染病防护和医院感染防控工作。
A joint medical expert group composed of national, provincial and municipal experts will assess the wounded on a case-by-case basis, implement a one-man-one strategy, closely monitor the changes of injuries, adjust and improve the treatment plan dynamically, give full treatment to them and strictly carry out the work of preventing and controlling infectious diseases among medical personnel.
事故发生时正在进行房屋改装作业据新华社消息，记者从泉州市有关方面了解到，酒店楼体坍塌事故系房屋改装作业时发生，该楼房业主目前已被公安部门控制。
According to Xinhua News Agency, the reporter learned from Quanzhou City that the collapse of the hotel building occurred during the renovation work, the owner of the building is now under the control of the public security authorities.
泉州市鲤城区住建局局长张翼说，事发楼房占地5亩，建筑面积约7000平方米，共有7层，属于钢结构房屋。
The five-acre building, with a floor area of about 7,000 square meters, consists of seven floors and belongs to a steel structure, said Zhang Wing, the director of the Quanzhou City residence.
该建筑经查是2013年开始建设，2018年改造为欣佳酒店，并于当年6月开业，酒店有各类客房计66间。
The building, which was built in 2013, was converted into a Xin Jia Hotel in 2018 and opened in June of the same year.
该建筑一楼共有6间，其中两间原为超市。
There are six rooms on the ground floor of the building, two of which were supermarkets.
今年春节前，房屋业主将一楼出租的超市收回重新改装。
Before the Spring Festival this year, the owner of the first floor of the supermarket to remodel.
3月7日晚上7时，房主接到现场施工人员电话称，在进行作业的一楼房屋一根柱子发生变形。
On 7 March, at 7 p.m., the owner received a telephone call from the construction staff at the site stating that a post had been deformed in the first floor of the house where the work was being carried out.
三四分钟后，楼体整体坍塌。
Three or four minutes later, the building collapsed.
张翼说，该楼房坍塌是因为装修还是原来结构问题，还需进一步甄别。
Zhang said the collapse of the building because of renovation or original structural problems, need to be further screened.
泉州市公安局局长李伙金告诉记者，房屋业主杨某某，65岁，为泉州本地人。
Quanzhou City Public Security Bureau Director Li Fengjin told reporters that the owner of the house Yang, 65 years old, Quanzhou native.
公安部门已传唤他到案。
The police have summoned him to the case.
